step.action:
If "status" keyword was provided: display dashboard and STOP (don't process):
=== Action Items Dashboard ===
| Status | Count | |--------|-------| | Open | {open_count} | | In Progress | {in_progress_count} | | Done | {done_count} | | Invalid | {invalid_count} | | Deferred | {deferred_count} |
Open Items by Priority: | ID | Title | Type | Priority | Age (sprints) | Source | Assignee | {for each open item, sorted by priority then age}
Aged Items (2+ sprints): {list of items open for 2+ sprints with escalation warnings}

Display on-screen report (NOT as a file):

    === Action Items Report ===

    Processed: {processed_count}
    Resolved: {done_count}
    Invalid: {invalid_count}
    Deferred: {deferred_count}
    In Progress: {in_progress_count} (stories created, awaiting sprint)
    Remaining: {open_count} (not yet processed)

    | ID | Title | Decision | Reasoning |
    {for each processed item: id, title, new status, brief resolution}

    {if in_progress_count > 0:}
    Stories created from action items:
    {list of new story keys with titles}
    These will be available in the next /kratos-sprint-plan.

    {if open_count > 0:}
    {open_count} items remain open. Run /kratos-action-items to continue processing.

    {if all resolved:}
    All action items resolved. Ready for /kratos-sprint-plan.
